subtitle: [Music]
electricity is the substance of a great
Cosmic deity that we call fohat the Lord
of universal electricity
the different aspects of the fohatic
energy are released into a world of
objectivity and cause the union or
separation of the different contents of
Consciousness we call Objects
electricity is a force which binds
balances or separates
electricity is really the relationship
between all things
without electricity there would be no
relationship
nor would there be any things
electricity is the means by which what I
call the ultimate particle events of
Cosmos
are aggregated or de-aggregated
aggregation produces form D aggregation
produces what we call formlessness
the energy which is behind aggregation
and de-aggregation and the steady state
which is neither
is electricity
the mysteries of electricity are deeper
than I know how to say
